			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_65305163">		
		on Monday April 14, 2025 @12:47PM (<span class="ind"></span><a rel="nofollow" href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23664879&amp;cid=65305163">#65305163</a>)
		<small><a href="//slashdot.org/~MightyMartian/journal/" title="Tuesday March 13, 2007 @03:39PM" class="user_journal_display">Journal</a> </small>
